name: RAGER - Demo
summary: Hand-picked by Meta for the Oculus Ignition Program, an honor extended to only a handful of VR projects, RAGER is the VR melee-rhythm brawler that hurls you into a roaring battleground, sets relentless robots on you, and lets hard-hitting music power every swing, block, and dodge—each move sparking to the beat as you rise to become the ultimate RAGER.
